    "description": "在<strong>Druidwalker</strong>，冬天就在眼前。森林进入了睡眠状态。你是一个德鲁伊，为森林的冬眠做准备。落叶的道路会把你带到哪里？<br><br>Druidwalker是一个实验性的游戏：你在游戏开始时不会得到提示。你必须与它互动，并在过程中弄清事情。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231060/extras/71c2c6ba705c61727c2321450163bbe1.poster.avif?t=1708453657\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231060/extras/71c2c6ba705c61727c2321450163bbe1.webm?t=1708453657\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2231060/extras/71c2c6ba705c61727c2321450163bbe1.mp4?t=1708453657\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>特点。<br>[list］<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 穿越森林，遇到动物；按你自己的节奏前进，不急于求成。<br></li><li> 手绘图像与传统器乐的结合<br></li><li> 宁静的roguelike游戏：在这里你不会输；没有死亡，只有在篝火旁的休息。<br></li><li> 短暂、轻松的体验，没有压力</li></ul>",
